l don't think l'm going
on this little expedition of yours.

25:23.200 --> 25:24.600
Oh, Dylan, please don't say that.

25:24.800 --> 25:26.300
Hey, l'm sorry,
we go to a school one day,

25:26.600 --> 25:28.500
