underprivileged kids,

25:28.800 --> 25:30.400
what kind of difference is that
gonna make?

25:30.700 --> 25:32.400
Well, l'm sorry you feel that way.

25:33.400 --> 25:35.200
Donna.

25:35.400 --> 25:38.200
