<i>Yeah, l see the dilemma,</i>

33:09.500 --> 33:11.400
<i>They got sidetracked</i>
<i>with their personal problems,</i>

33:11.700 --> 33:14.300
<i>No, excuse me,</i>
<i>but you don't know the real danger,</i>

33:14.600 --> 33:16.400
<i>Their bus is on a collision course</i>
<i>with a truck,</i>

33:16.700 --> 33:19.100
<i>l fixed that already,</i>
<i>l got that truck rerouted,</i>

