- <i>Which other truck?</i>
- <i>That other truck,</i>

33:46.100 --> 33:49.500
<i>Oh, so this guy,</i>
<i>Greg Clemons, is still</i>--

33:49.800 --> 33:52.100
<i>On the road to eternity,</i>

33:52.400 --> 33:54.800
<i>And so are those kids,</i>

34:11.300 --> 34:13.000
- Gil.
- Steve.

34:13.100 --> 34:15.800
Welcome to the Alvarado Street
