Donna,

38:16.000 --> 38:19.300
l brought my camera so if the
Madrigals want to sing another chorus,

38:19.600 --> 38:21.400
l can tape it.

38:32.900 --> 38:35.400
<i>She was too persuasive</i>
<i>for her own good,</i>

38:35.700 --> 38:37.800
<i>l can't bear to watch,</i>

